headline: RBC Capital Markets Maintains “Sector Perform” on Dover (DOV) Stock, Cuts PT
summary: Dover Corporation (NYSE:DOV) is one of the most profitable manufacturing stocks to buy now. On October 16, 2025, RBC Capital Markets maintained its “Sector Perform” rating on Dover while cutting the 12‑month price target to $183 from $206.
